inputs.name: example-cluster-3-e07ce395
inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 1
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-cluster-3-nodeLaunchConfiguration-e2c6720
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 1
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-01fd2aab1dc112845","subnet-0e1fa5519a3d93580","subnet-0bbb7b0a0d28731b4"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-cluster-3-eksCluster-238a5f7-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-cluster-3-eksCluster-238a5f7
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
